videos.description: Vanderbilt's Tommy Openshaw makes a 52-yard field goal to give the Commodores a 3-0 lead over North Carolina State.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Openshaw gets on the board with 52-yard FG

videos.description: With NC State facing fourth and goal from the one yard line, Matthew Dayes gets stopped for a three yard loss turning the ball over to Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt stuffs NC State on fourth and goal

videos.description: Jaylen Samuels makes the catch at the 4-yard line, breaks a tackle and then dives to the goal line for the NC State touchdown, putting the Wolfpack up 7-3.
videos.headline: Samuels breaks a tackle and dives for NC State TD

videos.description: Trent Sherfield run for 45 yds to the NCSt 11 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Trent Sherfield breaks out for 45 yard run

videos.description: Already with one receiving touchdown in the game, Jaylen Samuels takes the screen pass and turns on the jets, going 55 yards to the house to increase NC State's lead to 14-3.
videos.headline: Samuels goes 55 yards for his second TD of the game

videos.description: NC STATE Head Coach Dave Doeren expresses frustration over 1st half officiating
videos.headline: NC STATE Head Coach Dave Doeren expresses frustration over 1st half officiating

videos.description: Reggie Gallaspy II run for 5 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Reggie Gallaspy II punches in the 5-yard touchdown

videos.description: Having already scored on a screen pass once in the game, Jaylen Samuels takes another screen and goes to the house from 17 yards out, his third touchdown of the game, to increase NC State's lead to 28-3.
videos.headline: Samuels makes it three TDs on the day for NC State

videos.description: Ralph Webb run for 30 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Ralph Webb explodes for 30-yard touchdown run

videos.description: A.J. Cole III punt for 44 yds , Kalija Lipscomb returns for 71 yds to the NCSt 4
videos.headline: Kalija Lipscomb 71-yard punt return sets up VANDY inside the NC STATE 5

videos.description: Khari Blasingame run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: Khari Blasingame punches in the 1-yard TD

videos.description: Just when Vanderbilt was getting back into the game, Nyheim Hines takes the kickoff and weaves his way through the defense before finding open field and turning on the jets to go 100 yards for the kickoff return touchdown for NC State.
videos.headline: Hines goes 100 yards in a flash for kickoff return TD in NC State's win

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur pass intercepted for a TD Niles Clark return for 32 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Niles Clark returns INT for a 32-yard TD on the final play of the game

videos.description: After defeating Vanderbilt to win the Independence Bowl, NC State receives its trophy and coach Dave Doeren offers his take on the team's victory.
videos.headline: NC State receives trophy for winning Independence Bowl

videos.description: Jaylen Samuel's 3 TD performance fuels NC STATE to victory in the Camping World Independence Bowl
videos.headline: Jaylen Samuel's 3 TD performance fuels NC STATE to victory in the Camping World Independence Bowl
